data.description: Charming condominium in Sun City West. Street facing, end unit. 2 bedroom, 1.75 bath has 1221 of living space (Does not include sq footage of AZ room). Clean and bright home has all the comforts. Ceiling fans throughout, tile through out the home, carpet in bedrooms. Tube light in living room, Corian counter tops in kitchen.   Lovely Arizona room leads to covered, enclosed patio with relaxing little fountain and brick pavers.  A nice home in the heart of Sun City West.
